OL,3,CWood cutting company fined after
OL,4,Cowner's son killed in on site accident
OL,6,FA wood-cutting company in
OL,7,FNottinghamshire has been fined #22,500
OL,8,Fafter the owner's son was killed in an
OL,9,Faccident on site.
OL,11,FTom Brooke, 31, who was a director of
OL,12,Fthe family business, died when he was
OL,13,Fstruck by a load-lifting vehicle in
OL,14,F2019.
OL,16,FJohn Brooke Sawmill was prosecuted
OL,17,Funder health and safety laws.
