OL,6,FThe company previously pleaded guilty
OL,7,Fto a charge under the Health and
OL,8,FSafety Act and was also ordered to pay
OL,9,F#44,227.25 costs.
OL,11,FNottingham Crown Court heard Health
OL,12,Fand Safety Executive investigators
OL,13,Ffound "unsafe practices" when they
OL,14,Fvisited the site in Widmerpool after
OL,15,Fthe father-of-one died.
OL,17,FJudge Stuart Rafferty KC said:
