OL,6,F"Him and Rupert were incredibly close.
OL,7,FHe was just wonderful to be about, he
OL,8,Fwas a family man who worked hard.
OL,10,F"I don't think any sentence would ever
OL,11,Fcompensate for Tom's death and Tom not
OL,12,Fbeing here. I think it's more about
OL,13,Fclosure and accountability today for
OL,14,Fme. The fine is almost immaterial."
