OL,6,FDavid James, mitigating, said:
OL,7,F"Following the HSE's site visit in
OL,8,F2019, as soon as these issues were
OL,9,Frecognised, the company rectified
OL,10,Fthem. They properly instructed a
OL,11,Fhealth and safety expert to ensure
OL,12,Fsafety on site. It lost #100,000 a
OL,13,Fmonth income since a biomass plant
OL,14,Fcancelled its contract.
