OL,6,F"This site is entirely different now
OL,7,Fto how it was in 2019 and that is
OL,8,Fentirely down to Emma Brooke, who is a
OL,9,Fdirector of the company and the sister
OL,10,Fof Tom Brooke. There are speed bumps,
OL,11,Fadditional signs, two-way radio and
OL,12,Fany movement on site is monitored."
OL,14,FTom's sister Emma paid tribute to him
OL,15,Foutside court saying: "It was just
OL,16,Fhorrendous, I was there and I
OL,17,Fwitnessed it at the time, it's a
OL,18,Fliving nightmare.
