OL,6,F"Hopefully today is the end of one bit
OL,7,Fof it and we can put Tom to rest; he
OL,8,Fwas a brilliant brother and a
OL,9,Fbrilliant father and we miss him every
OL,10,Fday".
OL,12,FThe Health and Safety Executive said
OL,13,F"This has been a very difficult case
OL,14,Ffor all concerned. However, those in
OL,15,Fcontrol of work have a responsibility
OL,16,Fto implement safe methods of working.
OL,17,FHad simple measures been taken, this
OL,18,Ftragedy could have been prevented."
